For installing PyWPS:
    
1) unzip the archive with the program

    $ tar xzf pywps-0.1.tgz


2) Run the installation script
    
    $ cd pywps-0.1
    $ python setup.py install

3) Make symlink to wps.py file in your cgi-bin directory

    $ ln -s /usr/bin/wps.py /usr/lib/cgi-bin/wps.py

4) Update your configuration in etc/setup.py and etc/grass.py

5) See doc/install.pdf/txt/html for more details
